      hideCloseButton: false,
      arrowPosition: 30,
      backgroundClassName: 'phoney',
      arrowStyle: 2
  };

  var myLatlng = new google.maps.LatLng(41.730289,-81.186578);
  var marker = new google.maps.Marker({  position: myLatlng,   title:"EAGLE DESIGN &amp; CONSTRUCTION"});
  marker.setMap(map);
}

        impression_tracking(chamber_id, chamber_code, chamber_name, js_session_id);
      });
  }

  
  if ('') $('#show_browser_popup').click();
  if ('') show_browser_popup();

  // Track all impressions in one go
  if('' &gt; 0) track_bulk_impression('');
});


function show_browser_popup() {

    type: 'inline',
    content: '#browseHappyPopup',
    'onStart': function() {
      $('body').addClass('paused');
    }
  });
  $('#fancybox-wrap').css('background-color','transparent');
  $('#fancybox-content').css({'background-color':'#7ebb24'});
  $('#fancybox-outer').css({'border':'none','padding':'0','background-color':'transparent'});
  $('#fancybox-close').css('right','-14px');
}


// For Right Sidebar
// Fixed issue by @MS - 20140319
$(window).load(function() {

  if ($("#sidebarRightNew")[0]) {
    if ($('#sidebarRightNew').length) { // make sure "#sticky" element exists
      var el = $('#sidebarRightNew');
      var stickyTop = parseInt($('#sidebarRightNew').offset().top); // returns number
      var footerTop = parseInt($('#footer').offset().top); // returns number
      var stickyHeight = parseInt($('#sidebarRightNew').outerHeight());
      var launchMessage = parseInt($('.launchMessage').height());
      var topSpc = launchMessage ? (stickyTop - launchMessage) : stickyTop;
      var limit = footerTop - stickyHeight;

      var pos;
      var topPos;

      //console.log(stickyTop);

      $(window).scroll(function() { // scroll event
        var windowTop = parseInt($(window).scrollTop()) + stickyTop; // returns number
        if (stickyTop == windowTop) {
          el.css({ top: stickyTop });
          //console.log('1: '+stickyTop);
        }
        else if (limit &lt; windowTop) {
          var endLimit = limit - windowTop + topSpc;
          el.css({ top: endLimit });
          //console.log('2: '+endLimit);
        }
        else if (stickyTop &lt; windowTop) {
          pos = stickyTop - (windowTop - stickyTop);
          topPos =  (pos &gt; topSpc) ? pos : topSpc;
          el.css({ position: 'fixed', top: topPos });
          //console.log('3: '+topPos);
        }
        else {
          el.css({ position:' fixed'});
          //console.log('4');
        }
        //console.log(windowTop);
      });
    }
  }
});
